## xCoinMoney
xCoinMoney is a Bitcoin, Litecoin and Dollars online wallet that allows you to receive and send instant payments in  bitcoin, litecoin and dollars. xCoinMoney has two account types:  personal account and business account. 

### Fee
xCoinMoney have a very low transaction fee https://www.xcoinmoney.com/info/pricing  for business account and for personal account. Our service can be used for creating subscriptions and recurrent payments.

### Features

* Callback notification including Tor sites.
* Bitcoins, Litecoins and dollars are supported for instant payments and subscriptions.
* Instant internal payments of Bitcoin/Litecoin.
* 100% Anonymous payment. No verification of account is required.
* Personal and Business accounts are supported.
* Sending and paying invoices
* Advanced API.

